headline: Nasdaq (NDAQ) to Benefit From Secular and Cyclical Tailwinds
summary: Nasdaq Incorporated (NASDAQ:NDAQ) is one of the 12 oversold financial stocks to invest in according to hedge funds. On January 30, Michael Cyprys from Morgan Stanley maintained his Overweight rating on Nasdaq Incorporated (NASDAQ:NDAQ). The analyst also raised his target price on the stock from $113 to $116, implying 46% upside. Cyprys appreciates secular tailwinds […]

headline: 2 of Wall Street’s Favorite Stocks with Promising Prospects and 1 That Underwhelm
summary: The stocks in this article have caught Wall Street’s attention in a big way, with price targets implying returns above 20%. But investors should take these forecasts with a grain of salt because analysts typically say nice things about companies so their firms can win business in other product lines like M&A advisory.
